  <brief_title>Latent Tuberculosis in Second Generation Immigrants From High Risk Countries Compare to Low-risk Young Israeli Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>Better Identification of Latent Tuberculosis Infection Among Israeli Young Adults by Comparison Skin Tests and Interferon Gamma Releasing Assays (IGRA)</official_title>
